pageTitle: PGA West Norman, PGA West Norman Golf Course in La Quinta CA
textBeforeTable: The PGA West Norman golf course was made in the image of its creator, and Greg Norman, a.k.a. "the Shark," is known for an aggressive style of play. On the PGA West Greg Norman golf course, the risk-reward ratio is highly correlated and those who spend strokes on safe shots may wind up feeling like shark chum. Yet, Norman insists the measure of great PGA West course is playability for a variety of levels.
